<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Nouvelle demande de prestation</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Serif+Display&family=DM+Sans:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,500;0,600;1,300&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  </head>
  <body style="margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #EDEAE4; font-family: 'DM Sans', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;">

    <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background-color: #EDEAE4; padding: 48px 20px;">
      <tr>
        <td align="center">
          <table role="presentation" width="580" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="max-width: 580px; width: 100%;">

            <!-- Brand Header -->
            <tr>
              <td style="text-align: center; padding-bottom: 36px;">
                <span style="font-family: 'DM Serif Display', Georgia, serif; font-size: 22px; color: #1C1917; letter-spacing: -0.5px;">{{ brandName }}</span>
              </td>
            </tr>

            <!-- Main Card -->
            <tr>
              <td style="background-color: #FDFCFB; border-radius: 4px; overflow: hidden; border: 1px solid #E8E3DC;">

                <!-- Top accent line -->
                <div style="height: 3px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, #1C1917 0%, #44403C 50%, #A8A29E 100%);"></div>

                <!-- Header -->
                <div style="padding: 40px 56px 36px; border-bottom: 1px solid #F0EDE8;">
                  <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
                    <tr>
                      <td style="vertical-align: middle; width: 52px;">
                        <div style="width: 44px; height: 44px; border-radius: 50%; background-color: #EFF6FF; border: 1.5px solid #BFDBFE; text-align: center; line-height: 44px; font-size: 18px;">📋</div>
                      </td>
                      <td style="vertical-align: middle; padding-left: 16px;">
                        <p style="margin: 0 0 2px; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-transform: uppercase; color: #6B7280;">Nouvelle demande</p>
                        <p style="margin: 0; font-family: 'DM Serif Display', Georgia, serif; font-size: 26px; color: #1C1917; letter-spacing: -0.5px;">Demande de prestation</p>
                      </td>
                    </tr>
                  </table>
                </div>

                <!-- Body -->
                <div style="padding: 36px 56px 40px;">

                  <!-- Greeting -->
                  <p style="margin: 0 0 24px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.7; color: #44403C; font-weight: 300;">
                    Bonjour <span style="font-weight: 600; color: #1C1917;">{{ providerName }}</span>,
                  </p>
                  <p style="margin: 0 0 32px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.75; color: #57534E; font-weight: 300;">
                    Nous vous adressons une nouvelle demande de prestation. Veuillez trouver ci-dessous le détail de la mission ainsi que le lien direct vers le ticket associé sur notre plateforme.
                  </p>

                  <!-- Ticket Info Block -->
                  <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin-bottom: 28px;">
                    <tr>
                      <td style="background-color: #F8F7F5; border: 1px solid #E8E3DC; border-radius: 4px; padding: 24px 28px;">

                        <!-- Ticket ID + Priority row -->
                        <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin-bottom: 20px;">
                          <tr>
                            <td style="width: 50%;">
                              <p style="margin: 0 0 3px; font-size: 10.5px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 1.2px; text-transform: uppercase; color: #9CA3AF;">Référence ticket</p>
                              <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 600; color: #1C1917; font-family: 'DM Serif Display', Georgia, serif;">{{ ticketId }}</p>
                            </td>
                            <td style="width: 50%; text-align: right; vertical-align: top;">
                              <span style="display: inline-block; padding: 4px 12px; background-color: #FEF3C7; border: 1px solid #FDE68A; border-radius: 3px; font-size: 11.5px; font-weight: 600; color: #92400E; letter-spacing: 0.3px;">{{ priority }}</span>
                            </td>
                          </tr>
                        </table>

                        <!-- Divider -->
                        <div style="height: 1px; background-color: #E8E3DC; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>

                        <!-- Fields grid -->
                        <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">

                          <!-- Row 1 -->
                          <tr>
                            <td style="width: 50%; padding-bottom: 18px; vertical-align: top;">
                              <p style="margin: 0 0 3px; font-size: 10.5px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 1.2px; text-transform: uppercase; color: #9CA3AF;">Type de prestation</p>
                              <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 400; color: #1C1917;">{{ serviceType }}</p>
                            </td>
                            <td style="width: 50%; padding-bottom: 18px; vertical-align: top;">
                              <p style="margin: 0 0 3px; font-size: 10.5px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 1.2px; text-transform: uppercase; color: #9CA3AF;">Site / Localisation</p>
                              <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 400; color: #1C1917;">{{ location }}</p>
                            </td>
                          </tr>

                          <!-- Row 2 -->
                          <tr>
                            <td style="width: 50%; padding-bottom: 18px; vertical-align: top;">
                              <p style="margin: 0 0 3px; font-size: 10.5px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 1.2px; text-transform: uppercase; color: #9CA3AF;">Date souhaitée</p>
                              <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 400; color: #1C1917;">{{ requestedDate }}</p>
                            </td>
                            <td style="width: 50%; padding-bottom: 18px; vertical-align: top;">
                              <p style="margin: 0 0 3px; font-size: 10.5px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 1.2px; text-transform: uppercase; color: #9CA3AF;">Contact demandeur</p>
                              <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 400; color: #1C1917;">{{ requesterName }}</p>
                              <p style="margin: 2px 0 0; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 300; color: #78716C;">{{ requesterEmail ?? '' }}</p>
                              <p style="margin: 2px 0 0; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 300; color: #78716C;">{{ requesterPhone ?? '' }}</p>
                            </td>
                          </tr>

                          <!-- Row 3 – Description full width -->
                          <tr>
                            <td colspan="2" style="vertical-align: top;">
                              <p style="margin: 0 0 3px; font-size: 10.5px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 1.2px; text-transform: uppercase; color: #9CA3AF;">Description de la demande</p>
                              <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.7; font-weight: 300; color: #44403C;">{{ description }}</p>
                            </td>
                          </tr>

                        </table>
                      </td>
                    </tr>
                  </table>

                  <!-- Divider -->
                  <div style="height: 1px; background-color: #F0EDE8; margin-bottom: 28px;"></div>

                  <!-- CTA Section -->
                  <p style="margin: 0 0 20px; font-size: 13.5px; line-height: 1.6; color: #78716C; font-weight: 300; text-align: center;">
                    Accédez au ticket pour consulter les détails complets, poser vos questions ou mettre à jour le statut.
                  </p>

                  <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 16px;">
                    <a href="{{ ticketUrl }}"
                       style="display: inline-block; padding: 15px 40px; background-color: #1C1917; color: #FDFCFB; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 3px; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.5px;">
                      Voir le ticket →
                    </a>
                  </div>

                  <!-- Secondary link -->
                  <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 32px;">
                    <a href="{{ platformUrl }}" style="font-size: 13px; color: #78716C; text-decoration: underline; font-weight: 300;">
                      Accéder à la plateforme
                    </a>
                  </div>

                  <!-- Notice -->
                  <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
                    <tr>
                      <td style="background-color: #F0F9FF; border: 1px solid #BAE6FD; border-radius: 4px; padding: 14px 18px;">
                        <table role="presentation" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
                          <tr>
                            <td style="font-size: 15px; padding-right: 10px; vertical-align: top; padding-top: 1px;">ℹ️</td>
                            <td style="font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6; color: #0C4A6E; font-weight: 300;">
                              Merci de confirmer la prise en charge de cette demande dans un délai de <strong style="font-weight: 600;">{{ responseDelay }}</strong>. En cas d'indisponibilité, veuillez nous le signaler au plus tôt.
                            </td>
                          </tr>
                        </table>
                      </td>
                    </tr>
                  </table>

                </div>

              </td>
            </tr>

            <!-- Footer -->
            <tr>
              <td style="padding: 32px 20px 0;">
                <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
                  <tr>
                    <td style="border-top: 1px solid #D6D3CD; padding-top: 24px; text-align: center;">
                      <p style="margin: 0 0 6px; font-size: 12.5px; color: #A8A29E; font-weight: 300;">
                        Cet e-mail a été généré automatiquement par la plateforme {{ brandName }}.
                      </p>
                      <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 12px; color: #C4BFB8; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: 0.2px;">
                        © {{ new Date().getFullYear() }} {{ brandName }} · Tous droits réservés
                      </p>
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                </table>
              </td>
            </tr>

          </table>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>

  </body>
</html>